            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1615909485817-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1615909485817-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>green tomato chutney</strong>,<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl – this is your<strong> chutney dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1615909501839-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1615909501839-x400.jpg",
